{"tid":482552,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"因為玩pubg同一個識左十年既朋友嘈交","createTime":"2017-11-28T09:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T04:20:31.000Z","uid":68626,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bf115e30abc4e0fe5ba0a9b73743f961931ec3","tid":482552,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"其實我平時同佢性格都唔係幾夾<br />\n即係我係多變似水 柔則如西施含撚 暴則怒濤衝天既人<br />\n佢就好似一舊木咁 唔鐘意變化<br />\n今日同佢雙排個陣<br />\n嘈係邊到落已經嘈左好耐<br />\n最後我死死氣跟佢落<br />\n點知比佢執左把kar98 問我有冇8倍鏡<br />\n但係佢技術麻麻 我就話無 得兩倍 但其實我有<br />\n不過裝左落把m4到<br />\n去到最後一兩圈得番幾丁友個陣 我比人爆頭殺左<br />\n跟住佢執我裝見到個8倍鏡 講左句屌你老母<br />\n最後開無雙殺晒對面 成功食雞<br />\n不過完左場就block左我<br />\n應該點做好"},{"pid":"02f4da8180c9fb7a129d374d95a3a9fe95960cdf","tid":482552,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能"},{"pid":"eb5b4a7bdea321984bc3418ba94d0d054ed849af","tid":482552,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"好賤 識左十幾年 為左塊鏡 而講大話"},{"pid":"cec1e89cede66930a16a45078fe7415c618b2f89","tid":482552,"uid":43101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"打機打到嘈交真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573325fb4ecff4df60e8612baf6fd275079b62fe","tid":482552,"uid":111661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:38:14.000Z","msg":"講大話 抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd281c2419c6f6a46aef3d7800722fef54cc8037","tid":482552,"uid":111661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:38:56.000Z","m